001package io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.selenium;
002
003import io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.base.ComponentType;
004import io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.toggle.ToggleService;
005
006/**
007 * Represents a UI element for toggle switch components within the framework.
008 *
009 * <p>This interface extends {@link UiElement} and provides a default implementation
010 * for retrieving the associated component type, ensuring that toggle elements
011 * can be interacted with in a standardized manner.
012 *
013 * <p>Toggle switches allow users to enable or disable specific settings in the UI.
014 * This interface facilitates automation of toggle interactions, such as activation,
015 * deactivation, and state validation.
016 *
017 * @author Cyborg Code Syndicate üíçüë®üíª
018 */
019public interface ToggleUiElement extends UiElement {
020
021   /**
022    * Retrieves the component type associated with this toggle element.
023    *
024    * <p>The default implementation returns {@link ToggleService#DEFAULT_TYPE},
025    * ensuring that the toggle element is recognized as part of the toggle service.
026    *
027    * @param <T> The component type.
028    * @return The component type associated with this toggle element.
029    */
030   @Override
031   default <T extends ComponentType> T componentType() {
032      return (T) ToggleService.DEFAULT_TYPE;
033   }
034
035}
